data.description: Looking for peace and quiet? This beautiful country brick ranch with 1 Acre of land could be your perfect retreat! This house was completely torn down to the studs in 2018 and rebuilt with an additional 600 sq ft added to the house with a 36 x 40 shop. New well pump and wiring, and new water heater 2023. The house has a large covered front porch that is perfect for taking in the awesome view across from the home where you can see for miles! The open floor plan creates an inviting space with all updated flooring (no carpet), countertops, and cabinets. The primary bedroom is huge and has plenty of room for a sitting area. This property has no deed restrictions and would be the perfect place to go completely off grid. Just South of Bentonville, this commute is easy! Come and see it today!
